snippet.title: 7 Early Signs That Amber Heard Was Lying About Johnny Depp!
snippet.description:
💙 7 Early Signs That Amber Heard Was Lying About Johnny Depp!
Johnny and Amber’s love life and married life were not as appealing as their dramatic divorce is. 
Depp has steadily denied the claims of abuse by Amber Heard but was once again withheld approval to petition the court's ruling in March 2021. Court of Appeal jurists said the original hearing "was full and fair" and that the trial judge "gave thorough reasons for his conclusions which have not been determined even arguably to be revoked by any error of approach or errors of law."
Before I tell you about the bad times, let me tell you about the vigorous times. After several years of dating, Depp and Heard were wedded in 2015 in a secret ceremony in their home in LA. And ya, that’s the end of it.
